HEADER$$

$$BODY
<h3>Animal Statistics</h3>
<p></p>
<p>Please provide your intake numbers for kittens (less than 6 months) and cats (more than 6 months) for the previous year:  Kittens: <b>$KittensIntake</b> Cats: <b>$CatsIntake</b> </p>
<p></p>
<p>Please provide your total intake numbers for kittens aged 0 - 8 weeks for previous year: <b>$Under8WeekIntake</b></p>
<p></p>
<p>How many of the 0-8 week old kittens were born in care during the previous year: <b>$BornInCare</b></p>
<p></p>
<p>Please provide your intake numbers for kittens aged 0 - 4 weeks for previous year: <b>$Under4WeekIntake</b></p>
<p></p>
<p>Please provide your intake numbers for kittens aged 4 - 8 weeks for previous year: <b>$Between4And8week</b></p> 
<p></p>
<p>How many kittens  0 - 8 weeks old were euthanized in the previous year: <b>$Euthanised</b></p>
<p></p>
<p>How many kittens  0 - 8 weeks old died in care in the previous year: <b>$DiedInCare</b></p>
BODY$$

